p.k: Iron Pat Lola’s mother has just received the latest prototype for a food processor to test. Even though Lola promises to wait till evening before trying it the little girl switches it on just to see what it can do. But the kitchen device takes hold of Hoodie and...
p.d: Despite his small size and playful attitude, Pat is the hero that flies to his friends' rescue while avoiding numerous obstacles that get in his way.
